<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Stericycle started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Stericycle started.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers analyst Mark G. Banta said he initiated coverage of Stericycle Inc with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- &quot;We believe Stericycle's proprietary ETD technology positions the company to gain substantial market share going forward, which, in turn, will drive the company's revenue growth and boost facility operaing margins,&quot; Banta said in a research note.</p>
<p>-- EDT is an acronym for the Electro-Thermal-Deactivation treatment process which destroys harmful pathogens -- microorganisms that cause disease -- without producing noxious airborne emissions.</p>
<p>-- Shares were up 1/2 at 8-1/8.</p>
